@actionslacks if it was for CHIPS, yes the Verus Agama didn't recognise the address
but it should work fine for other coins
thats why we made this guide: https://support.komodoplatform.com/support/solutions/articles/29000029965-moving-chips-to-a-new-address

@load you have to search the address on DGB explorer to see if the funds are still there
don't open the old agama
then use the verus agama or other wallets to transfer funds to a new wallet(seed)

@angrygnat yes you can enter the old seed in Verus Agama
it is safe
but don't use that old address as receiving address in the future
